3:50:50.000Z","msg":"我都係戒晒所有糖，食野走汁同埋飲好多水。我諗我用多你一倍時間係我做少你好多運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我主要係踢波同埋踩單車。我目標同你差唔多，想減到65KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3ad81aa2a65b838db55ec61253fd25074db997","tid":2216704,"uid":323030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d24d9611ef8cc9c525fdb24293cddd91cc6456fb","tid":2216704,"uid":178205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af99166a0c42a65795cf48cd3e8492dc7c21113c","tid":2216704,"uid":323030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f4258877a5b5d16d8cfb66085d6236f66ceb70cd","tid":2216704,"uid":178205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經成日餓又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都瘦唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"試試蛋白質減肥法<br />\n暫時我都唔會肚餓<br />\n<br />\n目標 減多40-50磅<br />\nBTW, 記得要做運動/郁動下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"出街點食好?3隻茶葉蛋?<br />\n<br />\n運動我就2份兼職，係中間搭車要行少少路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇力郁，一番屋企就瞓，踩單車都無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"出街揀肉食(原型食物好緊要)<br />\n唔好太多汁喇 普普通通食扒都得<br />\n最緊要唔好捱餓姐<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現夜晚食完之後就忍口去訓教<br />\n唔好成日口痕痕食其他野就得"},{"pid":"e1b234451b9094ee6a342db24ff5d8f8dacef13a","tid":2216704,"uid":245549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27d5f8306bb0970382ad1373a4c29f798b99ea17","tid":2216704,"uid":178205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"我又係唔食早餐 晏晝食飯 夜晚烚菜<br />\n不過2個禮拜好似無乜變化<br />\n晏晝再食少就肚餓集中唔到精神，可能要食淨肉，戒埋啲碳水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"食得太低卡路里，小心反彈"},{"pid":"398c35ff72b0abec9d58b80c5058877347b4ee65","tid":2216704,"uid":16468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"我自己試過16:8 同 OMAD 都幾有效<br />\n16:8果時Lunch 淨係食雞扒沙律<br />\n夜晚食正常到正常偏多<br />\n不過都係低碳水同戒糖<br />\n<br />\nOmad 就lunch 都cut埋佢<br />\n<br />\n果排帶氧唔算特別多 但係間唔時會踩下單車當駁腳咁<br />\n(後來因為某d 原因, 瘋狂食食食同唔做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家又要減過)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESVXx6i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESVXx6i.png&h=3f537acc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}